Module Storage¶

storage.create_commonroad_scenario(current_node, simulation_param, lead_vehicle_param, acc_vehicle_param)[source]¶

Creation of a CommonRoad scenario

Parameters

  • current_node (Node) – node of the last time step which is used for scenario generation

  • simulation_param (Dict[~KT, ~VT]) – dictionary with simulation specific parameters

  • lead_vehicle_param (Dict[~KT, ~VT]) – dictionary with physical parameters of the leading vehicle

  • acc_vehicle_param (Dict[~KT, ~VT]) – dictionary with physical parameters of the ACC vehicle

storage.store_results(end_node, simulation_param, acc_vehicle_param, lead_vehicle_param, rrt_param, acc_param_complete)[source]¶

Saving calculated lead vehicle trajectory and falsification configuration

Parameters

  • end_node (Node) – node of the last time step which is used for profile generation

  • simulation_param (Dict[~KT, ~VT]) – dictionary with simulation specific parameters

  • acc_vehicle_param (Dict[~KT, ~VT]) – dictionary with parameters of the ACC-equipped vehicle

  • lead_vehicle_param (Dict[~KT, ~VT]) – dictionary with physical parameters of the lead vehicle

  • rrt_param (Dict[~KT, ~VT]) – dictionary with RRT-specific parameters

  • acc_param_complete (Dict[~KT, ~VT]) – dictionary with parameters of the ACC control algorithms
